data.description: **Seller offering $5,000 concession to help buy down the interest rate**. Don't miss your chance to see this beautiful home in the sought-after Fair Oaks Estates addition in North Richland Hills. This single story home is full of upgrades including fresh paint, new quartz countertops in the kitchen, and new carpet throughout the home. The open floor plan features two living rooms, a dining area, 4 bedrooms, and 2 full bathrooms. Huge kitchen has a beautiful island and a breakfast nook. You can't beat the backyard oasis that is private and full of mature shade trees making this perfect for entertaining.  Enjoy walking on the nearby Barton Walking Trails, or enjoy the playgrounds, picnic tables and pavilions at Dr Pillow Park less than a half mile from the home.
